## Development

### Setup Development Environment

```bash
python -m venv venv
source venv/bin/activate  # or venv\Scripts\activate on Windows
pip install -r requirements.txt
pip install -e ".[dev]"
```

### Running Tests

```bash
pytest
pytest --cov=xbrl_parser --cov-report=html
```

### Code Quality

```bash
# Type checking
mypy xbrl_parser/

# Formatting
black xbrl_parser/

# Linting
flake8 xbrl_parser/
```

